            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Every time you sustain damage, add your fury dice (d4) to your character sheet, up to a maximum of one fury dice. Your maximum fury dice increases by one during each class advancement. When you successfully hit with a melee attack, add any of your fury dice on your character sheet to the damage of the attack.",
