          },
          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "You may jump 3 spaces without drawing an opportunity attack and make a melee attack with a two-handed weapon. While jumping, you may leap over any human sized creature. If the target is killed, any remaining damage can be applied to any creature adjacent to the target.",
                "marks": [],
                "data": {}
              }
            ]
          },
          {
